  <block id="bc2fe31b1e2682a9a79513d792e9c721" category="doc">BlueXP现在是NetApp Console</block>
  <block id="995c8f79a8e07fbd8d519e45d03d6004" category="paragraph">NetApp Console建立在增强和重组的BlueXP基础之上，可在企业级内部和云环境中集中管理NetApp存储和NetApp Data Services，提供实时洞察、更快的工作流程和简化的管理，并且高度安全且合规。</block>
  <block id="2ef9d641d45afe99b74ad6f9a9f797ad" category="inline-link-macro">NetApp Console发行说明</block>
  <block id="800c173937521899b70a4ab5d735d3d7" category="paragraph">有关更改的详细信息，请参阅<block ref="b78e17cf58c4e309929c8d6a69594c7d" category="inline-link-macro-rx"></block>。</block>
