  <block id="691d3813e42d3c7a96ce16136d8f0585" category="section-title">切换到网格管理器</block>
  <block id="c7c42727522342992d0d5a7ac5aac3e9" category="paragraph">打开StorageGRID系统并选择网格管理器选项。</block>
  <block id="1da95130af2b7aa7e5215a16b692f80d" category="list-text">在右上角，选择*切换到网格管理器*。</block>
  <block id="7c1357c2af5a3afec56f643266c2d663" category="list-text">如果需要，请选择“返回”以通过控制台返回标准视图。</block>
  <block id="5ed613d5969e54b01e0691f040afb027" category="inline-link-macro">了解NetApp Console访问角色</block>
